# MI-Reactor-Planner

Nuclear reactor planner for [Modern Industrialization](https://github.com/AztechMC/Modern-Industrialization)

Planner is deployed on github pages: https://warbaque.github.io/MI-Reactor-Planner

## Reactor examples

- [Deuterium](https://warbaque.github.io/MI-Reactor-Planner/?i=3&)
    - 193k EU/t
    - Deuterium 157 mb/t
    - Plutonium 3.7/min

- [Tritium](https://warbaque.github.io/MI-Reactor-Planner/?i=3&)
    - 207k EU/t
    - Tritium 52 mb/t
    - Plutonium 4.9/min

- [Plutonium](https://warbaque.github.io/MI-Reactor-Planner/?i=3&)
    - 0 EU/t
    - Plutonium 20.5/min

- [EU/t](https://warbaque.github.io/MI-Reactor-Planner/?i=3&)
    - 264k EU/t
    - Deuterium 9 mb/t
    - Tritium 40 mb/t
    - Plutonium 12.7/min

- [EU/t without heat exchanger loop](https://warbaque.github.io/MI-Reactor-Planner/?i=3&)
    - 184k EU/t
    - Deuterium 45 mb/t
    - Plutonium 4.0/min

- [EU/t without heat exchanger loop](https://warbaque.github.io/MI-Reactor-Planner/?i=3&)
    - 214k EU/t
    - Deuterium 38 mb/t
    - Plutonium 6.5/min

- [60% efficiency](https://warbaque.github.io/MI-Reactor-Planner/?i=3&)
    - 105k EU/t
    - Deuterium 25 mb/t
    - Plutonium 1.0/min
